Watchdog
--------

If the hardware has an external watchdog reset circuit, an output needs to be assigned
to the external watchdog circuit.

+-----+-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
+ I/O | NAME              | DESCRIPTION                                              |
+-----+-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+
| O   | WDOG              | Watchdog enable/strobe                                   |
+-----+-------------------+----------------------------------------------------------+

